    • Commandline1

      public Commandline1() throws NotAValidMD5, java.io.IOException, NotValidOSSystem
      Creates 2 strings, one for each hashfunction Executes 5 commands (processes), if the command is one of two it will split on the space and add them to the strings. next it checks if the strings are the same, if they are the code continues if they are not the same a custom exception is thrown.

      NotAValidMD5
